Smoke Bombs
===========

Craft smoke bombs of any color with gunpowder, a water bottle, sand, and dye.
Recipe is shapeless. They can be thrown or placed into a dispenser.

Download .jar: https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/b5pfgqvavoi42j9/smokebombs-0.9.0.8.jar

Mod structure loosely based on Pahimar's [1] (which was based on KingLemming's?), but using IntelliJ IDEA.

[1] https://github.com/pahimar
